 were sold.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1007,10,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following table and answer the questions that follow&amp;mdash; Yearly Production (in thousand) of Scooters in Different Factories&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/1/215.8.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;552&quot; height=&quot;238&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;In which year was the total production of scooters of all factories 20% of the total production of scooters during 1985-1989?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;1988&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;1985&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;1986&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;1989&lt;/p&gt;','2','&lt;p&gt;The total production of scooters during 1985 &amp;ndash; 1989 = 115 + 108 + 149 + 102 + 101 = 575. &amp;there4;20% of 575 = 20/100 &amp;times; 575 = 115. Hence, it was the year of 1985.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1008,10,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following table carefully and answer the questions given below&amp;mdash; Number of Bales of Wool Processed by 5 Woollen Mills&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/1/215.9.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;591&quot; height=&quot;225&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Which mill has the processing of wool in March the highest percentage of the total processing by that mill during the five months period?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Polar&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Shepered&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Kiwi&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Warmwear&lt;/p&gt;','1','&lt;p&gt;Percentage processing of wool in the month of March by different mills. Polar = 1050/4500 &amp;times;100 = 23.33%. Shephered = 800/4100 &amp;times;100 = 19.51%. Kiwi = 1000/4900 &amp;times;100 = 20.40%. Warmwear = 1100/5450 &amp;times;100 = 20.18%. Comfy = 950/4350 &amp;times;100 = 21.83%. &amp;there4;The highest percentage is of the mill Polar.&lt;/p&gt;','Hard'),(1009,10,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following table carefully and answer the questions given below&amp;mdash; Number of Bales of Wool Processed by 5 Woollen Mills&lt;/p&gt;\