stions that follow:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%202%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/225.10.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;584&quot; height=&quot;380&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;In which match is the total runs scored by all the teams together the second highest?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Match 2 only&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Match 6 only&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Match 4 only&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Both Match 2 and Match 6&lt;/p&gt;','4','&lt;p&gt;It is second highest in both Match 2 and Match 4.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1148,11,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions that follow.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%202%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/225.11.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;481&quot; height=&quot;288&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;By how much amount are the sales in 1989 more than that in 1987?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 100&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 10,000&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 1&amp;sbquo;00,000&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 10&amp;sbquo;00,000&lt;/p&gt;','3','&lt;p&gt;Sales in 1989 = Rs. 420 thousands. Sales in 1987 = Rs. 320 thousands. &amp;there4;Required amount = Rs. (420 &amp;ndash; 320) &amp;times; 1000 = Rs. 100,000.&lt;/p&gt;','Easy'),(1149,11,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions that follow.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%202%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/225.11.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;481&quot; height=&quot;288&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;The sales in 1987 are how many times to that in 1988?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;0&amp;middot;8&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;1&amp;middot;25&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;8&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;0&amp;middot;25&lt;/p&gt;','1','&lt;p&gt;Let the required value is y, then 320 = 400y =&amp;gt; y = 320/400 = 0.8.&lt;/p&gt;','Easy'),(1150,11,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions