es in the year 2008?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 300 crore&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 400 crore&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 350 crore&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;Rs. 520 crore&lt;/p&gt;','2','&lt;p&gt;Average profit in 2008 is (350 + 400 + 450)/3 = Rs. 400 crore.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1298,12,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions given below:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%203%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/235.12.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;482&quot; height=&quot;290&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Profit earned by Three Companies over the years (Rs. in crore)&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;In which of the following years was the difference between the profits earned by company B and company A the minimum?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2003&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2007&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2005&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2008&lt;/p&gt;','2','&lt;p&gt;In 2007, the difference is only Rs. 25 crore.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1299,12,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions given below:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%203%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/235.12.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;482&quot; height=&quot;290&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Profit earned by Three Companies over the years (Rs. in crore)&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;In which of the following years was the total profit earned by all three companies together the highest?&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2004&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2007&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2008&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;2009&lt;/p&gt;','4','&lt;p&gt;It is highest in 2009. The value is 400 + 425 + 475 = Rs. 1300 crore.&lt;/p&gt;','Medium'),(1300,12,'4','&lt;p&gt;Directions: Study the following graph carefully and answer the questions given below:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;tinymce/uploaded/DI%20-%20Chapter%203%20-%204%20-%20DPPS/235.12.1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;482&quot; height=&quot;290&quot; /&gt;&